{
  "stem": "942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before I-- we leave town, I'd like to come back to our neighbor, who was a-- [CLEARS THROAT] a very good friend of ours, [CLEARS THROAT] a Christian lady.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[COUGHS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since we were orthodox, and as long as we had this nanny living with us, you know, so in the winter, she was starting the fireplaces so that we wouldn't freeze, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if you're an Orthodox Jew, you must not light a fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the law is that you cannot do any work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she was lighting the fires, you know, in our quarters, my grandfather, and my uncle and aunt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when she had to leave in 1939, well, this friend of ours, she was doing this for us, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And otherwise, I don't know what we could have done.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just can't figure, you know, how we would have lived, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there was no such thing as central heating, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Every home was heated by wood stoves and such.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she was a very great help to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The closest Gentile friend--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would think so, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yep.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a-- I can't think of any others, offhand, that-- there was nobody that was that close to us, that she-- you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so here we are, we're going back to the schoolhouse where we are being taken out of the schoolhouse this one morning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All of the Jewish people from this town, approximately 300 of us, altogether, men, women, children, and we're marched through town, guarded by gendarmes and taking-- we are taken down to the train station, and we're loaded up on a train.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This time, it was just a regular train.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
